{
  "id": "69b08bc1a9361b383ff3ecad",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:正規表現というもの",
  "created": 1773177833,
  "updated": 1773179783,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b08bc1a9361b383ff3ecad",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:正規表現というもの",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177833,
      "updated": 1773177833
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be8000000000047dd4c",
      "text": "放課後の教室。3人の高校生が机を囲んで雑談している。テーマは「[正規表現]」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177833,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd4d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd4e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd4f",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも！今日のテーマは〜……正規表現！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd50",
      "text": "プログラムとかでよく見るやつ。なんか「[呪文]」みたいな文字列のやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773179778
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd51",
      "text": "`^[a-z]+$` とかさ。初見だとガチで[暗号]じゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773179783
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd53",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd54",
      "text": "まあ……そのような記号の並び、たしかに不思議な詩のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd55",
      "text": "文字たちが秩序をもって並び、意味を見つけていく……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd56",
      "text": "まるで、文章の中から特定の言葉を探す司書のようでございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd58",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd59",
      "text": "概念としては近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5a",
      "text": "[** 正規表現（Regular Expression）]は、文字列のパターンを定義する形式言語。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5b",
      "text": "テキスト検索・入力チェック・置換などに使う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5c",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5d",
      "text": "https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Regular_expressions",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd5f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd60",
      "text": "おー、りかの説明、いつも通りクールで助かる〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd61",
      "text": "つまりさ、「こういう形の文字を見つけてね！」っていうルールを書くやつだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd62",
      "text": "たとえば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd63",
      "text": "`cat`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd64",
      "text": "って書いたら「cat」探すだけだけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd65",
      "text": "`c.t`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd66",
      "text": "って書くと cとtの間に何か1文字あるやつ全部OK！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd67",
      "text": "`cat`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd68",
      "text": "`cut`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd69",
      "text": "`cot`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6a",
      "text": "みたいな。便利〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6d",
      "text": "正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6e",
      "text": "`.` は「任意の1文字」を意味するメタ文字。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd6f",
      "text": "正規表現では、こういう[** 特殊文字（メタキャラクタ）]が多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd70",
      "text": "例",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd71",
      "text": " `.` 任意の1文字",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd72",
      "text": " `*` 0回以上繰り返し",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd73",
      "text": " `+` 1回以上",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd74",
      "text": " `[]`文字集合",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd75",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd76",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd77",
      "text": "まあ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd78",
      "text": "文字たちに役割があるのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd79",
      "text": "まるで舞台の役者のように、それぞれが決められた振る舞いをする……（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7c",
      "text": "あや、それ表現エモいｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7d",
      "text": "あとさ！個人的に一番「うおっ」ってなるのがこれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7e",
      "text": "`[0-9]+`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd7f",
      "text": "数字いっぱい探すやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd81",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd82",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd83",
      "text": "分解すると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd84",
      "text": "`[0-9]` → 0〜9のどれか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd85",
      "text": "`+ `→ 1回以上",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd86",
      "text": "つまり 連続した数字。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd87",
      "text": "例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd88",
      "text": "今日は気温23度",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd89",
      "text": "から`23`を抽出できる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8c",
      "text": "あら、それは便利ですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8d",
      "text": "文章の中から数字だけを取り出す……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8e",
      "text": "まるで物語の中から宝石を拾い上げるような作業ですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd90",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd91",
      "text": "あやの例え、毎回ファンタジーなんよｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd92",
      "text": "でも正規表現ってさ……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd93",
      "text": "だんだんヤバい呪文になるのが難点だよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd94",
      "text": "例えばメールチェックとか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd96",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd97",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd98",
      "text": "メールの正規表現は有名な例。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd99",
      "text": "かなり複雑になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9a",
      "text": "例（簡略）:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9b",
      "text": "`^[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+.[A-Za-z]{2,}$`",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9c",
      "text": "これは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9d",
      "text": "メールアドレス形式かどうかを判定する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dd9f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda0",
      "text": "うわ出たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda1",
      "text": "ラスボス呪文！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda2",
      "text": "初めて見たとき",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda3",
      "text": "「人間が書いたのこれ？」って思ったｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda5",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda6",
      "text": "確かに……少々、暗号めいておりますわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda7",
      "text": "けれど、規則がわかれば読み解ける……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda8",
      "text": "それは古い文献を解読するのにも似ております。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047dda9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddaa",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddab",
      "text": "実際、正規表現は理論計算機科学にも関係する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddac",
      "text": "形式言語理論では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddad",
      "text": "正規言語 ←→ 正規表現 ←→ 有限オートマトン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddae",
      "text": "という対応がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddaf",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb0",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regular_expression",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773179742
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb3",
      "text": "出たよ理系魔法ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb4",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb5",
      "text": "機械が文字をチェックするルールの数学版って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb8",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddb9",
      "text": "テキスト処理を高速に行うための理論基盤。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddbb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddbc",
      "text": "文字を探す技術の背後に、そんな深い理論があるのですね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddbd",
      "text": "本棚の静かな一冊にも、長い歴史が宿っているように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddbe",
      "text": "知れば知るほど、言葉というものは奥深いものですわね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddbf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc1",
      "text": "今日のまとめいくよー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc2",
      "text": "正規表現とは！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc3",
      "text": " 文字のパターンを決めるルール",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc4",
      "text": " 検索とか入力チェックで使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc5",
      "text": " `.` や` *` とか特殊文字がある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc6",
      "text": " でもたまに呪文になるｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc7",
      "text": "こんな感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddc9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddca",
      "text": "補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddcb",
      "text": "正規表現は覚えるより、使いながら調べる方が実用的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddcc",
      "text": "実務でもそのスタイルが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddcd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddce",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddcf",
      "text": "学びとは、少しずつ慣れていくものですものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd0",
      "text": "焦らず、一文字ずつ……（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd3",
      "text": "よーし！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd4",
      "text": "じゃあ次回のテーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd5",
      "text": "SQL？AI？それともGit？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd6",
      "text": "技術トーク回、地味に楽しいんだがｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08be9000000000047ddd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177834,
      "updated": 1773177834
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08bec000000000047ddd8",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177836,
      "updated": 1773177849
    },
